title: Mexican singer to be sent to South Carolina for assault case
text: > Entertainment Mexican singer to be sent to South Carolina for assault case FILE - This Aug. 6, 2014 photo shows Mexican singer Larry Hernandez posing for a photo during an interview in Los Angeles. Hernandez who stars in a Spanish-language TV show was arrested at Ontario Airport on a warrant out of South Carolina, authorities said Monday, Sept. 28. Hernandez, 38, was taken into custody on suspicion of kidnapping, assault and assault and battery causing injury. (AP Photo/Richard Vogel, File)
